# Library Management System

A comprehensive full-stack application for managing a physical lending library, integrating both front-end and back-end functionalities.



## Features

- In-memory indexing for optimized book retrieval
- RESTful API for seamless front-end and back-end integration
- Robust server-side input validation using Zod
- Dynamic UI components with React
- MongoDB integration for data persistence
- CRUD operations for efficient book management
  endpoints.

## Technologies Used

- Frontend: React, TypeScript
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js, TypeScript
- Database: MongoDB
- Validation: Zod
- Testing: Jest




